snippet.title: Johnny Depp vs Amber Heard: domestic violence & the fear of not being believed
snippet.description:
Just my thoughts on the leaked audios of Johnny Depp and Amber Heard. What are your thoughts? How has it impacted you? 

You can read the transcripts of the audios and watch the videos here: 
https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-7947733/Amber-Heard-admits-hitting-ex-husband-Johnny-Depp-pelting-pots-pans-tape.html

----
